language=EN>DeAdvocate</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/18/02 10:29:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11592.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Thought Horror Overfiend</span><hr size=1> Hey. I'm part of an up and coming guild, and we are looking for targets to progress on. We are looking at going for the Thought Horror Overfiend. Now, I searched a bit, but I couldn't find anything, so I was wondering if you guys could help. I just need some basic information:<br><br>How hard does he hit, and how fast? (Triple, quad, etc.)<br>Is he slowable?<br>Does he rampage/flurry? <br>Is he particularly resistant to anything?<br><br>If someone could toss those facts over a bit, I'd appreciate it greatly <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Not asking for a strat, just want to know those things before we get ourselves into this <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br><br>---Lucianno Pavarottii <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/urobdrinalbrown.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RobDrinalBrown</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/18/02 11:22:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11592.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Thought Horror Overfiend</span><hr size=1> &quot;How hard does he hit, and how fast? (Triple, quad, etc.)&quot;<br><br> No clue really as I don't get hit often by him. 600-700? I think quad.<br><br>&quot;Is he slowable?&quot;<br><br> Yes, and since you can slow him out melee range; he is way gimped. He was at least a challange before he was rooted. Unslowed he can hurt.<br><br>&quot;Does he rampage/flurry?&quot;<br>Flurry, I believe. sorry been awhile<br><br>&quot;Is he particularly resistant to anything?&quot;<br><br> Pretty damn melee resistant. the fight will take you a fairly long time. <br><br><br> He also has two diferent ae's. both are curses which do not stack. Meaning if he can only land one of em on you at a time and they both last a long time. One is a melee type ae and the other is a healer\caster type ae. You will need remove curse or greater remove curse for the caster type ae. The melee type ae can only be dispelled. <br><br> Try him out and you should come up with a sound strat to down him fairly easily. Remember he's a long arse fight. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udeadvocate.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DeAdvocate</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/18/02 11:24:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11592.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Thought Horror Overfiend</span><hr size=1> Thanks a bunch for the response <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uslapussz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SlapusSZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/18/02 11:28:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11592.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ~</span><hr size=1> getting past the elders are the hardest part.  Debuff him slow him.  before you engage.  Melees get feeblemind.  Casters get overfiends fury.  game over <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uskrills.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Skrills</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/19/02 1:38:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11592.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~</span><hr size=1> Cant stress Elders enough.  THO himself is a wuss but getting through the Elders can be a pain. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/urufuskf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>RufusKF</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/19/02 10:15:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11592.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ~</span><hr size=1> I've seen an SK tank him for his full health and a gimpy ranger (haha kaidan thats you) tank him until he was at 40%... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uarafain.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arafain</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font 